title: Names folders
creator: Zarlox
content:
Hello,

I am using french version of thunderbird for Android.

On my Gmail account, the word "[GMAIL]" appears before some names folders ("brouillon", "corbeille", "spam" and "tous les messages"). Also, on Gmail but also other clients like Hotmail, all created folders have the word "INBOX" before there name.

Is there a fix to this situation ?

Thank you for your time.
